title: The Slow Press — Issue 14
meta: | type: newsletter | date: 2025-04-19
byline: Edited by Mara Velasquez
epigraph: Read slowly. The world is in a hurry. — Anonymous
dedication: For everyone who marks passages in pencil.

section: On reading
text: There is a particular pleasure in returning to a book you already know.
