caption: A reader's shelf in Lisbon.
footnote: 1 — See also: Alberto Manguel, Chapter 7.

section: Letters
text: A reader in Porto writes to ask whether rereading counts as reading at all.
quote: A bookshop is a vote of confidence in a neighborhood. | by: Editor